original: Kullberg, Karl-Erik Jean, tandläkare, Vadstena, f. 29/12/19 i Motala av Jean K. o. Annie Sundstedt. G. 44 m. Inga-Lisa Edström. Barn: Lena f. 45. — Stud:ex. i Motal’a 38, tandil :-kand. 40, tandl:ex. 44. Distr :tandl. i Smålandsstenar 44-45, assist, där 45- 46, praktik i Vadstena sed. 46.
translated: Kullberg, Karl-Erik Jean, dentist, Vadstena, born on December 29, 1919 in Motala to Jean K. and Annie Sundstedt. Married in 1944 to Inga-Lisa Edström. Children: Lena, born in 1945. - Graduated from high school in Motala in 1938, dental education in 1940, dental exam in 1944. Was a dentist in Smålandsstenar from 1944 to 1945, assistant there from 1945 to 1946, and has been practicing in Vadstena since 1946.
